rfect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11feccc07120ab4c9654689c45418fbc653e0a7d","tid":354341,"uid":125382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:13:39.000Z","msg":"同個frd去行山 佢著呢種鞋 我著普通運動鞋<br />\n行啲沙石又上又落<br />\n我行到腳跛 佢健步如飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bdd5a54937fcff8428680a714e96b6c4b6bcb2","tid":354341,"uid":79471,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:17:34.000Z","msg":"發覺哩家只要話人係毒撚就立於不敗之地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de514c8b40718288d5762b17cca42ad8f1561f6d","tid":354341,"uid":117647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>後生著呢啲出街唔係行山的話十成九係毒撚<br />\n我認我歧視 吹呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲做工程都會著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n工程佬唔係著果d安全鞋咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你會唔會係辦公室都著安全鞋啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申番緊工程做顧問公司 好多同事都係著依d鞋。其實簡簡單單配番件普通T恤 長褲 已經好好睇，需要落site既時候咪換安全鞋，超級方便。"},{"pid":"a2da46d68c7de29c49deb58be969853ef44d1d04","tid":354341,"uid":12979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:37:41.000Z","msg":"著緊danner ml ii<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6c6dbf9f7bed6cf3d20ff6703d7732c3711fff","tid":354341,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雖然唔型但都幾貴吓  colombia賣緊都幾千<br />\n<br />\n透氣  防水</blockquote><br />\n認真個款就真係差左d columbia 幾千真心唔值 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />danner salomon asolo aku d款靚好多</blockquote><br />\ndanner行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你行埋我個份